    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Experience the perfect balance of performance and reliability with this meticulously maintained vehicle. Representing exceptional value in today\u2019s market, this car has been thoroughly inspected to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for safety and roadworthiness. The exterior retains a sharp, polished look, while the interior offers a clean and comfortable environment for both driver and passengers. This is a dependable choice for those who demand quality and longevity. Schedule your test drive today to appreciate the smooth handling and solid build that make this a standout selection on our lot.",
      "price": 34900.0,
