      "description": "Hey there! If you're looking for a reliable companion that still turns heads at the stoplight, you've found her. I've absolutely loved every mile in this beauty, and she\u2019s been treated like one of the family. She\u2019s got a few tiny signs of a life well-lived\u2014just minor character marks really\u2014but she runs like a dream and is ready for her next big adventure. I'm only letting her go to make some space in the driveway, and I'd love to see her go to someone who appreciates a smooth, soulful drive as much as I do. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
